  ],
  "remarks": "Shandong Yulong Petrochemical Co., Ltd. operates a refinery in the People’s Republic of China. It is a significant buyer of Russian oil, having bought millions of barrels of oil from the Eastern Siberia-Pacific Ocean oil pipeline and the Urals. The energy sector, in particular the oil sector, is a sector providing substantial revenue to the Russian Government. Therefore, Shandong Yulong Petrochemical Co., Ltd. is involved in an economic sector providing a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation.",
